com.camerontec.catalys.server.adapter.solace

Class SolaceRawTransformer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.server.adapter.solace.SolaceRawTransformer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFromMessageTransformer, IMessageTransformer, IToMessageTransformer, ISolaceMessageTransformer

    public class SolaceRawTransformer
extends Object
implements ISolaceMessageTransformer
    IMessageTransformer implementation for transforming messages between Catalys and Solace where each Solace message is a BytesMessage whose payload is a byte[].

    Internally this uses StandardFixTransformer.

    Each instance of this class will have its own buffers. And since SolaceMessageSource and SolaceMessageListener instances are bound to their respective sessions, buffer contents will not be shared between sessions (FSD-66869).
